{"type":"message","id":"93be6a23","parentId":"29fa722b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:29:08.003Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-22 22:29:07 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54cb85fdb0a8b38397caf62f6e5]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54cb85fdb0a8b38397caf62f6e5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"sender\": \"章彦博\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-22 22:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"name\": \"章彦博\"\n}\n```\n\n你帮我运行我看下"}],"timestamp":1774189748001}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c643714","parentId":"93be6a23","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:29:10.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我运行刚才安装的 nano-banana-pro 技能，看看它是什么功能。我需要先读取这个技能的 SKILL.md 文件来了解它的用途和使用方法。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_108aad30e13b4b7a89f66911","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/skills/nano-banana-pro/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":86,"cacheRead":10959,"cacheWrite":1257,"totalTokens":12308,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000024080000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000024740000000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774189748003}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7d05240","parentId":"0c643714","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:29:10.280Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_108aad30e13b4b7a89f66911","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: nano-banana-pro\ndescription: Generate/edit images with Nano Banana Pro (Gemini 3 Pro Image). Use for image create/modify requests incl. edits. Supports text-to-image + image-to-image; 1K/2K/4K; use --input-image.\n---\n\n# Nano Banana Pro Image Generation & Editing\n\nGenerate new images or edit existing ones using Google's Nano Banana Pro API (Gemini 3 Pro Image).\n\n## Usage\n\nRun the script using absolute path (do NOT cd to skill directory first):\n\n**Generate new image:**\n```bash\nuv run ~/.codex/skills/nano-banana-pro/scripts/generate_image.py --prompt \"your image description\" --filename \"output-name.png\" [--resolution 1K|2K|4K] [--api-key KEY]\n```\n\n**Edit existing image:**\n```bash\nuv run ~/.codex/skills/nano-banana-pro/scripts/generate_image.py --prompt \"editing instructions\" --filename \"output-name.png\" --input-image \"path/to/input.png\" [--resolution 1K|2K|4K] [--api-key KEY]\n```\n\n**Important:** Always run from the user's current working directory so images are saved where the user is working, not in the skill directory.\n\n## Default Workflow (draft → iterate → final)\n\nGoal: fast iteration without burning time on 4K until the prompt is correct.\n\n- Draft (1K): quick feedback loop\n  - `uv run ~/.codex/skills/nano-banana-pro/scripts/generate_image.py --prompt \"<draft prompt>\" --filename \"yyyy-mm-dd-hh-mm-ss-draft.png\" --resolution 1K`\n- Iterate: adjust prompt in small diffs; keep filename new per run\n  - If editing: keep the same `--input-image` for every iteration until you’re happy.\n- Final (4K): only when prompt is locked\n  - `uv run ~/.codex/skills/nano-banana-pro/scripts/generate_image.py --prompt \"<final prompt>\" --filename \"yyyy-mm-dd-hh-mm-ss-final.png\" --resolution 4K`\n\n## Resolution Options\n\nThe Gemini 3 Pro Image API supports three resolutions (uppercase K required):\n\n- **1K** (default) - ~1024px resolution\n- **2K** - ~2048px resolution\n- **4K** - ~4096px resolution\n\nMap user requests to API parameters:\n- No mention of resolution → `1K`\n- \"low resolution\", \"1080\", \"1080p\", \"1K\" → `1K`\n- \"2K\", \"2048\", \"normal\", \"medium resolution\" → `2K`\n- \"high resolution\", \"high-res\", \"hi-res\", \"4K\", \"ultra\" → `4K`\n\n## API Key\n\nThe script checks for API key in this order:\n1. `--api-key` argument (use if user provided key in chat)\n2. `GEMINI_API_KEY` environment variable\n\nIf neither is available, the script exits with an error message.\n\n## Preflight + Common Failures (fast fixes)\n\n- Preflight:\n  - `command -v uv` (must exist)\n  - `test -n \\\"$GEMINI_API_KEY\\\"` (or pass `--api-key`)\n  - If editing: `test -f \\\"path/to/input.png\\\"`\n\n- Common failures:\n  - `Error: No API key provided.` → set `GEMINI_API_KEY` or pass `--api-key`\n  - `Error loading input image:` → wrong path / unreadable file; verify `--input-image` points to a real image\n  - “quota/permission/403” style API errors → wrong key, no access, or quota exceeded; try a different key/account\n\n## Filename Generation\n\nGenerate filenames with the pattern: `yyyy-mm-dd-hh-mm-ss-name.png`\n\n**Format:** `{timestamp}-{descriptive-name}.png`\n- Timestamp: Current date/time in format `yyyy-mm-dd-hh-mm-ss` (24-hour format)\n- Name: Descriptive lowercase text with hyphens\n- Keep the descriptive part concise (1-5 words typically)\n- Use context from user's prompt or conversation\n- If unclear, use random identifier (e.g., `x9k2`, `a7b3`)\n\nExamples:\n- Prompt \"A serene Japanese garden\" → `2025-11-23-14-23-05-japanese-garden.png`\n- Prompt \"sunset over mountains\" → `2025-11-23-15-30-12-sunset-mountains.png`\n- Prompt \"create an image of a robot\" → `2025-11-23-16-45-33-robot.png`\n- Unclear context → `2025-11-23-17-12-48-x9k2.png`\n\n## Image Editing\n\nWhen the user wants to modify an existing image:\n1. Check if they provide an image path or reference an image in the current directory\n2. Use `--input-image` parameter with the path to the image\n3. The prompt should contain editing instructions (e.g., \"make the sky more dramatic\", \"remove the person\", \"change to cartoon style\")\n4. Common editing tasks: add/remove elements, change style, adjust colors, blur background, etc.\n\n## Prompt Handling\n\n**For generation:** Pass user's image description as-is to `--prompt`. Only rework if clearly insufficient.\n\n**For editing:** Pass editing instructions in `--prompt` (e.g., \"add a rainbow in the sky\", \"make it look like a watercolor painting\")\n\nPreserve user's creative intent in both cases.\n\n## Prompt Templates (high hit-rate)\n\nUse templates when the user is vague or when edits must be precise.\n\n- Generation template:\n  - “Create an image of: <subject>. Style: <style>. Composition: <camera/shot>. Lighting: <lighting>. Background: <background>. Color palette: <palette>. Avoid: <list>.”\n\n- Editing template (preserve everything else):\n  - “Change ONLY: <single change>. Keep identical: subject, composition/crop, pose, lighting, color palette, background, text, and overall style. Do not add new objects. If text exists, keep it unchanged.”\n\n## Output\n\n- Saves PNG to current directory (or specified path if filename includes directory)\n- Script outputs the full path to the generated image\n- **Do not read the image back** - just inform the user of the saved path\n\n## Examples\n\n**Generate new image:**\n```bash\nuv run ~/.codex/skills/nano-banana-pro/scripts/generate_image.py --prompt \"A serene Japanese garden with cherry blossoms\" --filename \"2025-11-23-14-23-05-japanese-garden.png\" --resolution 4K\n```\n\n**Edit existing image:**\n```bash\nuv run ~/.codex/skills/nano-banana-pro/scripts/generate_image.py --prompt \"make the sky more dramatic with storm clouds\" --filename \"2025-11-23-14-25-30-dramatic-sky.png\" --input-image \"original-photo.jpg\" --resolution 2K\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774189750275}}
{"type":"message","id":"52c1cd0d","parentId":"e7d05240","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:29:14.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个技能是用于图像生成和编辑的。用户说\"帮我运行我看下\"，但没有提供具体的图像生成需求。我需要向用户确认他们想生成什么样的图片，或者是否有图片需要编辑。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**nano-banana-pro** 是一个图像生成和编辑技能 🎨，使用 Google 的 Nano Banana Pro (Gemini 3 Pro Image) API。\n\n**主要功能：**\n- 🖼️ **文生图** - 根据描述生成新图片\n- ✏️ **图生图** - 编辑现有图片（修改风格、添加/删除元素等）\n- 📐 **分辨率** - 支持 1K/2K/4K\n\n**要运行它，我需要你提供：**\n1. **图片描述** - 你想生成什么样的图片？\n2. **或者** - 如果你有要编辑的图片，提供图片路径和修改指令\n\n**示例：**\n- \"生成一张日出的海滩图片\"\n- \"把这张图片改成卡通风格\"（需提供图片路径）\n\n你想生成什么图片？🎨"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":231,"cacheRead":12216,"cacheWrite":1727,"totalTokens":14180,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00006468000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006534000000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774189750280}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b1c7a6d","parentId":"52c1cd0d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:29:17.510Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-22 22:29:17 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54cb850a64a4b21ddb86f6efd0b]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54cb850a64a4b21ddb86f6efd0b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"sender\": \"章彦博\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-22 22:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"name\": \"章彦博\"\n}\n```\n\n刚才安装的技能是干嘛的"}],"timestamp":1774189757508}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e6cc11c","parentId":"9b1c7a6d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:29:21.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问刚才安装的技能是干嘛的。我刚才已经读取了 SKILL.md 文件，可以直接回答这个技能的功能用途。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**nano-banana-pro** 是一个 **AI 图像生成和编辑技能** 🎨\n\n**核心功能：**\n- 🖼️ **文生图** - 用文字描述生成图片\n- ✏️ **图生图** - 编辑现有图片（改风格、加元素、调色等）\n- 📐 **多分辨率** - 支持 1K/2K/4K 输出\n\n**技术底层：**\n- 使用 Google 的 Gemini 3 Pro Image API\n- 需要 `GEMINI_API_KEY` API 密钥\n\n**典型用法：**\n```bash\n# 生成新图片\nuv run ~/.codex/skills/nano-banana-pro/scripts/generate_image.py --prompt \"一只在太空的猫\" --filename \"cat-space.png\"\n\n# 编辑图片\nuv run ... --prompt \"让天空更戏剧化\" --input-image \"original.jpg\" --filename \"edited.png\"\n```\n\n**工作流程：**\n1. 先用 1K 快速生成草稿\n2. 调整提示词迭代\n3. 满意后用 4K 生成最终版\n\n你有 API 密钥的话，我可以帮你生成一张图片试试 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":291,"cacheRead":12216,"cacheWrite":2302,"totalTokens":14815,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00008148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00008214}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774189757509}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb886d50","parentId":"1e6cc11c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:35:33.069Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-22 22:35:32 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54cbadf3f880b4ccbd3bc53d6b9, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54cbadf3f880b4ccbd3bc53d6b9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"sender\": \"章彦博\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-22 22:35 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"name\": \"章彦博\"\n}\n```\n\n我是一名AI算法工程师，我要做一篇openclaw的AI算法分享，根据我的指令一步一步完成：\n\n1. 请从全网搜下openclaw相关的算法详细解析内容（特别是官网），形成大纲和 ppt 内要展示的文字。\n\n2. 使用 nano-banana-pro 技能绘制 ppt 的每一页。\n\n3. 使用 wps-office 创建 ppt，然后把对应页的图片插入。\n\n4. 注意，需要封面和结束页，风格统一，学术化。"}],"timestamp":1774190133067}}
{"type":"message","id":"62c35cf0","parentId":"bb886d50","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:35:37.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我帮他完成一个 OpenClaw AI 算法分享的 PPT 制作任务，分为 4 个步骤。我需要先搜索 OpenClaw 相关的算法信息，然后再逐步完成后续任务。\n\n让我先从 web_search 开始搜索 OpenClaw 的相关信息。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来帮你一步步完成这个 OpenClaw AI 算法分享 PPT 的制作。\n\n## 第一步：搜索 OpenClaw 相关算法信息\n\n让我先搜索 OpenClaw 的官网和相关资料：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_3904981094c547f49baf56de","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"OpenClaw AI agent framework architecture algorithm"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_62662a2729d64baa9e34353e","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":15000,"url":"https://docs.openclaw.ai"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":213,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":15257,"totalTokens":15476,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000059640000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000603}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774190133069}}
