{"type":"message","id":"baa7e8a4","parentId":"add5ed1d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:40:41.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说得对，我不能因为遇到阻塞就停止输出。我应该：\n1. 承认错误\n2. 主动检查是否有其他方式继续（比如检查环境变量、配置文件）\n3. 或者换一种方式继续任务\n\n让我先检查一下是否有 GEMINI_API_KEY 的环境变量或配置文件，看看能不能找到密钥。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，我不应该卡住不输出。让我主动检查是否有可用的 API 密钥，或者换方案继续。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_7ca533e752b24702bfa27446","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"GEMINI_API_KEY: ${GEMINI_API_KEY:-(not set)}\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e9ac0f28c3da4784ad441dbb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/ 2>/dev/null | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_8f71ab7a54124516b0aee68d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":33871,"output":229,"cacheRead":10606,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44706,"cost":{"input":0.0037258100000000004,"output":0.00006412,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037899300000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774190434905}}
