{"type":"message","id":"08405e51","parentId":"944dc687","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:42:28.231Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我安装 PPT 生成插件，搜索结果显示有几个相关的技能，我需要把这些结果整理给用户，并推荐最合适的选项让他选择。\nClawHub 上找到了多个 PPT 生成技能！让我看一下详情：\n\n**搜索结果（按相关性排序）：**\n1. **ai-presentation-maker** - AI Presentation Maker ⭐3.49\n2. **generate-presentation** - Generate Presentation ⭐3.46\n3. **afrexai-presentation-mastery** - Presentation Mastery ⭐3.42\n4. **presentation-html-generator-skill** - HTML 生成器 ⭐3.38\n5. **presentation** - Presentation ⭐3.37\n6. **claw-presentation-creator** - Claw PPT 创建器 ⭐3.14\n7. **gamma-presentation** - Gamma PPT 生成器 ⭐3.07\n\n天工 AI 的 PPT 技能在 ClawHub 上没有找到，但有多个可选方案。\n\n**推荐方案：**\n\n| 技能 | 评分 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ai-presentation-maker | ⭐3.49 | 评分最高，功能全面 |\n| generate-presentation | ⭐3.46 | 直接生成 PPT |\n| claw-presentation-creator | ⭐3.14 | OpenClaw 原生风格 |\n\n**小王子，你想安装哪个？**\n\n我建议安装 **ai-presentation-maker**（评分最高），或者你告诉我具体需求，我帮你 inspect 一下技能详情再决定。","thinkingSignature":""}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":344,"cacheRead":43908,"cacheWrite":4522,"totalTokens":48780,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00009632000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00009698000000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774190541338}}
