{"type":"message","id":"89b1208b","parentId":"502cf79e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:43:14.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"有吗\"，是在问是否有天工相关的 PPT 技能。根据我刚才的搜索结果，ClawHub 上没有找到天工 (Tiangong) 相关的 PPT 技能。我需要明确告诉用户没有天工的，但有其他可选方案，并建议安装哪个。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"ClawHub 上**没有天工 AI 的 PPT 技能**。\n\n**但有其他可用的 PPT 生成技能：**\n\n| 技能 | 评分 | 推荐度 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| ai-presentation-maker | ⭐3.49 | ⭐⭐⭐ 最高分 |\n| generate-presentation | ⭐3.46 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| claw-presentation-creator | ⭐3.14 | ⭐⭐ OpenClaw 原生 |\n\n**我的建议：安装 `ai-presentation-maker`**（评分最高，功能最全面）\n\n要我直接安装吗？还是你先看一下这个技能的详情？\n\n```bash\nclawhub install ai-presentation-maker\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":227,"cacheRead":43908,"cacheWrite":5205,"totalTokens":49346,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00006356000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006422}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774190579399}}
