{"type":"message","id":"8a69674e","parentId":"33a1fe4e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:10:49.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给了密码但之前尝试有权限问题，让我重新尝试用正确的 sudo 密码方式来安装 WPS，分步骤进行：先下载 deb 包，然后用 sudo 安装。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"网络问题导致下载失败。**小王子，由于网络限制，WPS 官方源无法访问。**\n\n**建议方案：**\n\n1. **手动下载安装（推荐）：**\n   - 用浏览器访问：https://wps.cn/linux\n   - 下载 .deb 安装包\n   - 双击安装，或发给我文件路径我来安装\n\n2. **先用 LibreOffice：**\n   - LibreOffice Impress 已经打开了 PPT\n   - 功能足够编辑和演示\n   - 等 WPS 装好后再切换\n\n3. **或者用 Flathub 安装：**\n   ```bash\n   flatpak install flathub com.kingsoft.wps-office\n   ```\n\n你想选哪个？或者你现在能看到 LibreOffice 窗口吗？📊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":206,"cacheRead":69817,"cacheWrite":133,"totalTokens":70162,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000057680000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00005834}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774192244395}}
