{"type":"message","id":"9b2d27dc","parentId":"f4af1fe5","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:16:26.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"新 PPT 已生成成功，现在需要向用户确认完成并说明这个版本与之前版本的不同之处。\n✅ 硬核 AI 算法版 PPT 完成！\n\n**文件位置：** `/home/zhangyanbo/workspace/presentations/exports/OpenClaw_AI_核心算法 (硬核版).pptx`\n\n**11 页内容：**\n\n| 页码 | 主题 | 核心算法 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 1 | 封面 | - |\n| 2 | 目录 | - |\n| 3 | Context Engine | Ingest/Assemble/Compact/After Turn |\n| 4 | Compaction | Token 阈值/预压缩 Memory Flush |\n| 5 | Memory System | 双层架构/向量检索/Hybrid Search |\n| 6 | Session Pruning | Cache-TTL/Soft Trim/Hard Clear |\n| 7 | Model Failover | Profile Rotation/Cooldown 退避 |\n| 8 | System Prompt | 模块化/Bootstrap 注入 |\n| 9 | 性能优化 | Token 优化/Cache 友好/成本控制 |\n| 10 | 总结 | 性能指标 |\n| 11 | Q&A | - |\n\n---\n\n**对比旧版：**\n- ❌ 删除了网关架构/路由算法等工程内容\n- ✅ 聚焦 AI 核心算法（上下文/记忆/调度）\n- ✅ 加入具体配置参数和算法细节\n\n小王子，用 LibreOffice 打开这个新版看看？","thinkingSignature":""}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":83007,"output":332,"cacheRead":10606,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93945,"cost":{"input":0.00913077,"output":0.00009296,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00922373}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774192575180}}
